OL,3,C'Urgent' manhunt for escaped prisoner
OL,5,FPolice are "urgently" searching for a
OL,6,Fprisoner who has absconded from an
OL,7,Fopen prison.
OL,9,FDaniel Buckley, 37, was last seen at
OL,10,FHMP Thorn Cross in Appleton,
OL,11,FWarrington, on the morning of
OL,12,FSaturday, 30 May.
OL,14,FCheshire Police is carrying out
OL,15,Fextensive enquiries to track him down
OL,16,Fand is appealing to the public for any
OL,17,Finformation that could help locate him.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G1/4
