PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F396A1780585869
OL,3,C'Urgent' manhunt for escaped prisoner
OL,5,FA Prison Service spokesperson said:
OL,6,F"Public protection is our priority and
OL,7,Fprisoners who fail to return following
OL,8,Ftemporary release face strict
OL,9,Fpunishments, including a return to a
OL,10,Fclosed prison and being prevented from
OL,11,Fmoving to open conditions for up to
OL,12,Ftwo years.
OL,14,F"The police are working urgently to
OL,15,Frecapture this individual, and we urge
OL,16,Fanyone with information to go to the
OL,17,Fpolice."
OL,26,@yD@HO]
