OL,3,C'Urgent' manhunt for escaped prisoner
OL,5,FAnyone who sees Buckley should not
OL,6,Fapproach him but call Cheshire Police
OL,7,Fon 999, quoting IML-2340086, or
OL,8,FCrimestoppers anonymously on 0800 555
OL,9,F111.
